metadata.name: Site Launch Gen 01
metadata.description:
An appreciation piece to commemorate the Generation I collectors & the site launch. 

Digitization.wiki is an ongoing archive of non-digital, analog materials funded by web3 technology & stored on the IPFS. The project seeks to create new passageways that unify education & aesthetics. 

By publishing these pieces, we can provide a means of preserving these creatures online to raise awareness of our relationship with the internet, the planet, and its inhabitants. 

Each entry is hand-created using natural flora & fauna specimens.

With Love, 
NOCELLCOVERAGE


HTTPS://DIGITIZATION.WIKI
